rComments: One of the best profs I've ever had - completely brilliant - my hand hurt after every class trying to write down everything she said.

the material was quite interesting, but the prof was a bit boring. i think sometimes she forgot that it is NOT a law class, as some of the texts were quite technical, and she failed to provide much clarification. a plus was that there was no exam, just 2 assignments, and she does provide quick responses to emails.
A dedicated, hard-working, professor who is helpful in tackling difficult theoretical material.
